UOM Codes CODES FOR UNITS OF MEASURE USED IN INTERNATIONAL TRADE Revision 8 / 2012
(UNECE/CEFACT Trade Facilitation Recommendation No.20)

Source of Definitions: http://www.unece.org/cefact/recommendations/rec_index.htm

Examples:
---------

$uom_code   = uom_code::get_uom_code_from_measure('kg');

$measure    = uom_code::get_measure_from_uom_code('MTR');

$lookup_arr = uom_code::get_lookup_array();


